<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Ready - {{orderNumber}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35, #F7931E);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        
        .completion-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8, #f0f8f0);
            border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .completion-info h2 {
            color: #FF6B35;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .order-summary {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .order-summary h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #FF6B35;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .items-list {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .item-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .item-quantity {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .pickup-delivery-info {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #FF6B35;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .pickup-delivery-info h3 {
            color: #FF6B35;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .location-box {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px dashed #FF6B35;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .total-amount {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .total-amount h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .total-amount .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35, #F7931E);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .action-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .contact-info h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .contact-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .contact-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .contact-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #FF6B35;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #FF6B35;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .celebration {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 48px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            animation: bounce 1s infinite alternate;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            from { transform: translateY(0px); }
            to { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .info-row,
            .item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .contact-details {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .action-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üçΩÔ∏è {{restaurantName}}</h1>
            <p>Your Order is Ready!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="completion-info">
                <div class="celebration">üéâ</div>
                <h2>Great News, {{customerName}}!</h2>
                <p>Your delicious meal is ready and waiting for you!</p>
                <div class="status-badge">‚úÖ Order Completed</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-summary">
                <h3>üìã Order Details</h3>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Order Number:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">#{{orderNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Completed:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{completionDate}} at {{completionTime}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="items-list">
                    <h4 style="margin: 15px 0 10px 0; color: #555;">Items Prepared:</h4>
                    {{#each items}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div>
                            <div class="item-name">{{name}}</div>
                            <div class="item-quantity">Qty: {{quantity}}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="color: #4CAF50; font-size: 20px;">‚úì</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="total-amount">
                <h3>Total Paid</h3>
                <div class="amount">{{total}}</div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if isDelivery}}
            <div class="pickup-delivery-info">
                <h3>üöö Out for Delivery</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Your order is on its way to you!</p>
                <div class="location-box">
                    <strong>Delivery Address:</strong><br>
                    {{deliveryAddress}}
                </div>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-top: 15px;">
                    <em>Our delivery person will contact you shortly</em>
                </p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if isPickup}}
            <div class="pickup-delivery-info">
                <h3>üè™ Ready for Pickup</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Please come and collect your order!</p>
                <div class="location-box">
                    <strong>Pickup Location:</strong><br>
                    {{restaurantAddress}}
                </div>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-top: 15px;">
                    <em>Please bring your order number for quick service</em>
                </p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="tel:{{restaurantPhone}}" class="action-button">üìû Call Restaurant</a>
                <a href="#" class="action-button">‚≠ê Rate Your Experience</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h3>üìû Questions About Your Order?</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;">We're here to help!</p>
                <div class="contact-details">
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">üì±</div>
                        <div><strong>Phone</strong><br>{{restaurantPhone}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">üìç</div>
                        <div><strong>Address</strong><br>{{restaurantAddress}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center;">
                <h3 style="color: #4CAF50; margin-bottom: 10px;">üôè Thank You!</h3>
                <p>We appreciate your business and hope you enjoy your meal!</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><em>We'd love to hear about your experience - please consider leaving us a review!</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 {{restaurantName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You're receiving this email because you placed an order with us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
